{"tid":1559270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全港各大商場唱《願榮光歸香港》令運動再昇華","createTime":"2019-09-10T17:33:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T23:46:03.000Z","uid":80972,"like":60,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"543166f9c4df2e85a8ff2a3e11152329b60e22d1","tid":1559270,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:33:02.000Z","msg":"《願榮光歸香港》鞏固示威者個信心、身份認同不在講。仲可以進一步走入社區，拉攏民心。<br />\n<br />\n坦白講，港豬係會對破壞公物有反感，而林奠呢幾日將輿論帶去港鐵受損係做俾日日搭鐵嘅港豬睇。不嬲打仗都係「<span style=\"color: red;\">攻城為下，攻心為上</span>」。如果叫勇武抗爭係以剛制強，唱歌就係以柔攻心。效果可能更意想不到<br />\n<br />\n1) <span style=\"color: red;\">唱歌比叫口號感染民心</span>，歌詞中「自由」、「民主」、「正義」都係普遍香港人認同。個個宗教都普遍會有歌曲，就係因為歌曲最易感染人心。<br />\n<br />\n2) 三日唔埋兩日去商場唱歌令遊客更少、商戶唔高興，地產佬更大壓力，<span style=\"color: red;\">變相係另一個經濟攬炒</span>。我覺得集中去港鐵商場唱，比破壞港鐵更有效力。<br />\n<br />\n3) 或再引爆黑警核彈，黑警會再諗方法入去拉唱歌嘅人，咁和平嘅活動都比黑警搞，令黑警完全喺國際社會出醜，更多港豬好似721後咁認同運動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n願榮光歸香港<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c91ee86be8a597449e0eb0cafe76c98ec14d5a25","tid":1559270,"uid":80972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:34:00.000Z","msg":"自推1<br />\n願榮光歸香港"},{"pid":"038152152c58b54895f28ab54b2e53abfc500768","tid":1559270,"uid":80972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:35:12.000Z","msg":"自推2<br />\n願榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"94aa82a034244ed6691c5f5e2c32166005cb0dbe","tid":1559270,"uid":80972,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:35:53.000Z","msg":"自推3<br />\n願榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可"},{"pid":"89a4aaaf7e18ea66965f3e5fccc7cd5356420f6b","tid":1559270,"uid":296341,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:36:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e3af21f09f43489282bf6a38f9ded78572512b4","tid":1559270,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:55:09.000Z","msg":"自推4<br />\n願榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可"},{"pid":"bdbf68dd9cb751afde5b81388cb3f8c2df86bfad","tid":1559270,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:55:44.000Z","msg":"自推5<br />\n願榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可"},{"pid":"8b66906b2829eb3789e25c5ba10ae02291fdf927","tid":1559270,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:56:28.000Z","msg":"自推6<br />\n願榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可"},{"pid":"8d8e1775c7b4973f06d503b8233356a3ef848314","tid":1559270,"uid":111934,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:56:35.000Z","msg":"又激嬲一班玻璃心了<br />\n佢地又要漏夜開post 唱衰隻歌了"},{"pid":"1d6c4796b01682fa3245ffc6c4c5cd839f43642c","tid":1559270,"uid":270871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:57:05.000Z","msg":"P牌仔同意"},{"pid":"53940b99be2f29faa058cbb154d4164b1a70eb46","tid":1559270,"uid":274599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:57:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2af4926d3736443483041c73a1baf224242beb05","tid":1559270,"uid":15730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:57:38.000Z","msg":"最好就拉人唱歌 個畫面就好核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e471dacb16efb38c745b4b53f0fc7c37fcb77d9","tid":1559270,"uid":122666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:58:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fec0f821e7772292e41646623223160b51a3ec6a","tid":1559270,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:58:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"93e9fe94d6cdce3c8d8da9998b36a5f48e616291","tid":1559270,"uid":296084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:59:00.000Z","msg":"練多啲<img src